text: Tasha St. Louis (born 20 December 1983) is a Trinidadian footballer who plays as a midfielder. She has been a member of the Trinidad and Tobago women's national team, of which she is the top scorer of all time. ==International goals== Scores and results list Trinidad and Tobago' goal tally first. {| class="wikitable" |- !
